snippet.title: The Lord of the Rings: Return of the King -  E3 game Trailer (2003)
snippet.description:
The Lord of the Rings: Return of the King-  Official E3 2003 Game Trailer
Developed by Electronic Arts Redwood Shores Studio for Playstation 2 then ported to PC, Xbox, GameCube by Hypnos Entertaiment Inc.
Published in November 2003 by Electronic Arts  for PC (Windows), Playstation 2, GameCube, Xbox.
Published by Aspyr Media in March 2004 for Macintosh (ported by Beenox Shift).

Year : 2003
System : PC (Windows)/Gamecube/Playstation 2/Xbox/Macintosh.

Trailer found on the  Electronic Arts FTP server.
